text: I'm coming over from straight journalism (digital journo, skilled in multimedia, social, writing, editing etc). Have no idea what all these digital marketing acronyms mean. What is CXL?

text: Learn all their jobs if you do not know how to do it all already and be prepared to pitch in with your team to GSD. As a military leader (Master Sergeant E-7), when crunch time comes and the mission is at a critical point don't stand to the side and 'just supervise'. You will win absolute trust and credibility with your team if you jump into the fray too. All in it together for the common goal whatever that is.
